{"tid":1260482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩 出面咁多分化/帶風向既post","createTime":"2019-06-27T00:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T01:10:52.000Z","uid":61886,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e9b86b3c44abedf817a85cc5ebf88dbcb54cdb2","tid":1260482,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"一係就係話個灰衫警唔係想扮示威者衝擊<br />\n(即係警犬好驚比人拎住依個point打<br />\n我地更加要死捉依個point黎打)<br />\n<br />\n一係就係咁屌梁係鬼<br />\n大佬 又係大家共識無大台<br />\n又係咁話佢唔知去左邊<br />\n唔帶人走 累人比人拉<br />\n你地玩晒啦 做咩都比你地屌<br />\n(擺明係想玩分化)<br />\n今次衰左 係一個好好汲取教訓既經驗<br />\n幾時撒 都係一個智慧<br />\n<br />\n大家抖足精神<br />\n諗清楚<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不受傷 不被捕"},{"pid":"f0a066dd5abd24b82fb7875330fc36b7bfa00757","tid":1260482,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"推          <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=6607114b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n未爭取到五項訴求前，<br />\n香港人將「不撤不散」。<br />\n<br />\n五個訴求包括<br />\n1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法&nbsp;<br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動&nbsp;<br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪&nbsp;<br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行&nbsp;<br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/26/232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F26%2F232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png&h=8cfbbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">不撤不退！</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[文宣戰]抗爭告白心聲Poster，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳！！！！</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259733</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以入post睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好幫手推埋上熱門<br />\n等多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(想share但又懶既直接係最底copy再開！) </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"82c9fad42a6024c0f4cef068536d41120585d6de","tid":1260482,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3f3521ddb7e84a14035dce644a9c22e92057b5ea","tid":1260482,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:40:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"80852f537d0b98bff81468e6763e9e6ce0bb87c9","tid":1260482,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁唔係第一次失左踪，有前科</span>"},{"pid":"81c3217839ad33d6569af6f4b44c01b16118469d","tid":1260482,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80852f537d0b98bff81468e6763e9e6ce0bb87c9","tid":1260482,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁唔係第一次失左踪，有前科</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"點解仲會有大台思維<img src